channel.title: Eldrazi 604 release
channel.description:
I started this project with hope and confidence but when i released the public beta no one came on besides people i was talking to on skype so i have given up on this. I am releasing it. But don't get your hopes up i have added a anti leech and it isn't open source you must get a class editor i will not make it easy for you to take my hard work and get players out of it "cough....cough...boxrune"
Well here are some pictures this isn't even close to what i have added / fixed. I do not have time to upload 50+ pictures.
[IMG]http://imageflock.com/img/1297591720.bmp[/img]
[IMG]http://imageflock.com/img/1297591716.bmp[/img]
[IMG]http://imageflock.com/img/1297591712.bmp[/img]
Here is the download link i re-factored my client to work excellent i will not release it you must use the hellpvp 569 client. Find it yourself
[url=http://www.mediafire.com/?9u2brd0x78y06x7]Eldrazi server_files.rar[/url]
Thanks for looking. I am currently trying to find a project to work on I cannot be bothered to host a server for people to play on and criticize me for not fixing a bug that i missed or didn't have time to put into it.
